Front-End â€” todo-web (Next.js + Tailwind, TypeScript)
Prereqs

  Node 20+

Backend API running (see todo-api below)

Set NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL to your API base (default: http://localhost:4000)

Setup & Run
  # from repo root
  cp .env.local.example .env.local        # ensure API URL is correct
  pnpm i      # or: npm i
  pnpm dev    # http://localhost:3000

Build & Start
  pnpm build
  pnpm start
